title: Forbidden Affairs Vol. 8: My Best Friend's Husband
description: Forbidden Affairs Vol. 8: My Best Friend's Husband Its a delicate balance for Mona - keeping her best friend, Angela happy while juggling a secret affair with Angelas husband, Michael. Despite years of friendship, Mona just cannot control her desires and she indulges in a full blown affair behind Angelas back. Unsure how to navigate the tricky terrain, Mona seeks advice from her sister, Pristine - who somehow managed to successfully break up a marriage and land the man of her dreams. But, things become complicated for Mona when the guilt over betraying her best friend takes over. With some semblance of a moral compass, Mona breaks off things with Michael and starts dating another man. However, old habits die hard when Michael refuses to let Mona move on and the affair starts back up again - but not without consequences. Monas heart is bound to break - whether it be losing her best friend or her best friends husband - the man she cant help but love.
